Package: plskit
Type: Package
Title: PLS Regression with Modern Inference
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Paweł", "Lenartowicz", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "6quarg@gmail.com")
Description: PLS regression with modern inference: canonical
    percentile confidence intervals, calibrated permutation, and
    null-Bayesian split-half tests, alongside legacy outputs (BSR,
    VIP, jackknife) for compatibility with established workflows.
    R wrapper around the Rust 'plskit' engine via 'extendr'.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Cargo (>= 1.74)
